s or programs", "bbox": [788.8, 1180.0, 915.6, 1199.4]}, {"text": "Part II", "bbox": [544.4, 60.0, 692.5, 105.2]}, {"text": "Item 5.", "bbox": [127.5, 112.8, 235.9, 149.7]}, {"text": "Market for the Registrant’s Common Equity,", "bbox": [307.5, 112.8, 962.1, 149.7]}, {"text": "Related Stockholder Matters and Issuer Purchases of", "bbox": [307.5, 151.1, 1073.2, 188.1]}, {"text": "Equity Securities", "bbox": [307.5, 189.4, 559.3, 226.3]}, {"text": "Cincinnati Financial Corporation had approximately 13,000 shareholders of record and approximately", "bbox": [127.5, 230.8, 1037.3, 254.4]}, {"text": "36,000 beneficial shareholders as of December 31, 2009. Many of our independent agent representatives", "bbox": [127.5, 254.4, 1080.1, 278.0]}, {"text": "and most of the 4,170 associates of our subsidiaries own the company’s common stock. We are unable to", "bbox": [127.5, 278.0, 1080.3, 301.7]}, {"text": "quantify those holdings because many are beneficially held.", "bbox": [127.5, 301.6, 665.6, 325.3]}, {"text": "Our common shares are traded under the symbol CINF on the Nasdaq Global Select Market.", "bbox": [127.5, 331.5, 955.3, 355.2]}, {"text": "We discuss the factors that affect our ability to pay cash dividends and repurchase shares in Item 7,", "bbox": [127.5, 501.2, 1021.1, 524.9]}, {"text": "Liquidity and Capital Resources, Page 68. One factor we address is regulatory restrictions on the dividends", "bbox": [127.5, 524.9, 1079.4, 548.5]}, {"text": "our insurance subsidiary can pay to the parent company, which also is discussed in Item 8, Note 9 of the", "bbox": [127.5, 548.5, 1061.2, 572.2]}, {"text": "Consolidated Financial Statements, Page 106.", "bbox": [127.5, 572.1, 552.2, 595.8]}, {"text": "The following summarizes securities authorized for issuance under our equity compensation plans as of", "bbox": [127.5, 602.0, 1054.6, 625.7]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009:", "bbox": [127.5, 625.6, 318.9, 649.3]}, {"text": "The number of securities remaining available for future issuance includes: 7,354,695 shares available for", "bbox": [127.5, 914.9, 1072.2, 938.5]}, {"text": "issuance under the Cincinnati Financial Corporation 2006 Stock Compensation Plan, which can be issued", "bbox": [127.5, 938.5, 1071.5, 962.1]}, {"text": "as stock options, service-based, or performance-based restricted stock units, stock appreciation rights or", "bbox": [127.5, 962.1, 1062.5, 985.8]}, {"text": "other equity-based grants; 72,158 shares of stock options available for issuance under the Cincinnati", "bbox": [127.5, 985.8, 1031.9, 1009.4]}, {"text": "Financial Corporation Stock Option Plan VII  and 300,000 shares available for issuance of share grants", "bbox": [127.5, 1009.4, 1046.7, 1033.0]}, {"text": "under the Director’s Stock Plan of 2009, which was approved by shareholders during 2009. Additional", "bbox": [127.5, 1033.0, 1041.4, 1056.7]}, {"text": "information about stock-based associate compensation granted under our equity compensation plans is", "bbox": [127.5, 1056.7, 1059.5, 1080.3]}, {"text": "available in Item 8, Note 17 of the Consolidated Financial Statements, Page 113.", "bbox": [127.5, 1080.3, 857.2, 1103.9]}, {"text": "We did not sell any of our shares that were not registered under the Securities Act during 2009. The board", "bbox": [127.5, 1499.9, 1076.2, 1523.5]}, {"text": "of directors has authorized share repurchases since 1996. Purchases are expected to be made generally", "bbox": [127.5, 1523.5, 1062.8, 1547.2]}]}